DELETE FROM testimonials;

INSERT INTO testimonials (clientName, clientTitle, rating, testimonialText, serviceUsed, featured, approved)
VALUES 
('Michael Goldenberg', NULL, 5, 'I recently used All Resume Services and was impressed with their professionalism and attention to detail. I had thought about creating my own job application documents, but I quickly realized I needed professional help. The experience exceeded my expectations. The team provided me with up-to-date and modern documents suitable for any job. The price was worth every cent—it''s a great investment in your professional future. Communication was excellent, and they responded quickly to all my questions. I highly recommend All Resume Services to anyone looking for a professional, modern, and effective resume.', NULL, 1, 1),
('Jackson Misago', NULL, 5, 'Thanks Sonia, I am pleased with how my professional CV & cover letter turned out.', NULL, 1, 1),
('S. Muller', NULL, 5, 'Thank you Sonia for a wonderful Resume and cover letter. I will recommend you to my family and friends. I''m now confident applying for jobs. I can''t describe your work because it''s more than wonderful. I will be using All Resume Services in the future.', NULL, 1, 1),
('T. Zboncak', NULL, 5, 'Oi, just gotta tell you guys some awesome news! I actually scored the job I applied for! And guess what? I owe it all to All Resume Services! Those guys really knocked it outta the park. I''ve used them twice now and both times they''ve totally outdone themselves. Their work far exceeded my expectations and I was really impressed with how they prepared me for the interviews. I felt confident and well-prepared, which definitely helped me clinch the job. Huge thanks to Sonia and her team—you guys are legends!', NULL, 1, 1),
('Nigel Howarth', NULL, 5, 'I am so happy with the service that I received from All Resume Services, specifically Sonia & her team. They really know how to update/write a resume that makes you stand out from the crowd. I couldn''t believe how professional everything was, from the communication to the final product. Sonia asked me all the right questions to get to know my skills and experience, ensuring everything would look amazing. I have some friends that have used other resume writing companies in the past, but after seeing mine, they have serious resume envy! They wished they saved their money and gone with Sonia & her team. Who knew a resume could look so stunning? Mine is head and shoulders above the competition, and it''s all thanks to All Resume Services. Highly recommend!', NULL, 1, 1)
